{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He opened my father's store and said that this now belongs to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he did something he shouldn't have done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But my sister-in-law came back, and she asked me because I was living with another girlfriend of mine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She said that, no, no, this doesn't look good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You come and stay with me, with us, which I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And some of her sisters came back, so there was some sort of a community.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I-- I was really very much out of it for the whole month of this return.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Particularly, I was-- not only I, all the-- as the survivors began coming back, sort of dribbling in, we recognized a woman, a Hungarian woman walking with my dress, with my sister-in-law's shoes, with this, that.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I saw a woman there riding my bike, and it was terrible because, you know, it's mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, why did you come back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was given to us, and it was resentment on the part of the population for the Jews having come back and saying, hey, this is my armoire, as I found my-- my armoire in my own room with the Dandier.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so there was this kind of a terrible thing, and also the Russians were in charge because it was-- the Russians were the liberators.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember Stalin's huge pictures, looking very grandfatherly with the pipe in his mouth, you know, bedecking all the big buildings.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was-- it was very sad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very sad, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That morning when I was liberated, that beautiful May morning, I thought that when I'll come back home, people will throw flowers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Thank God that you survived, but this was not the case.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't want us back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, one day-- it was July, I believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
